HEADWORD: Exspuition
<hw>Ex`spu*i"tion</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>exspuitio</ets>; <ets>ex</ets> out + <ets>spuere</ets> to spit: cf.
F. <ets>exspuition</ets>.]</ety> <def>A discharge of saliva by
spitting.</def> <mark>[R.]</mark> <rj><au>E. Darwin.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
